%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20and%20iPhone%2015%20look%20and%20feel%20very%20similar%2C%20save%20for%20minute%20differences%20in%20dimension%20(the%20iPhone%2015%20is%20slightly%20taller).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20visual%20difference%20is%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20somewhat%20dated%20static%20display%20notch%2C%20which%20houses%20its%20Face%20ID%20sensors%20and%20front%20camera%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20iPhone%2015's%20sleeker%20Dynamic%20Island%2C%20a%20convenient%20shape-shifting%20module%20for%20interacting%20with%20apps%20and%20notifications.%20The%20iPhone%2016e%20also%20has%20a%20single%20camera%20on%20the%20rear%2C%20whereas%20the%20iPhone%2015%20has%20a%20dual%20camera%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20and%20iPhone%2015%20side%20by%20side%20on%20a%20wooden%20surface.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d1a0fa69253ccddf98fe11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20(left)%20has%20a%20display%20notch%20and%20slightly%20thicker%20borders%20compared%20to%20the%20iPhone%2015's%20(right)%20Dynamic%20Island%20and%20slightly%20narrower%20borders.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20black%20borders%20around%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20display%20are%20also%20slightly%20thicker%20than%20those%20on%20the%20iPhone%2015.%20Still%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20looks%20like%20a%20modern%20premium%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20and%20iPhone%2015%20have%20exactly%20the%20same%20buttons%2C%20including%20the%20Action%20button%20that%20replaced%20the%20iPhone's%20signature%20silent%20switch%20with%20the%20iPhone%2015%20series.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295fd99f5-8f72-4d71-a27f-2b0e89282bda%5C%22%3EiPhone%2016e%20vs.%20iPhone%2015%3A%20Performance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20benchmark%20results%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20running%20on%20Apple's%20latest-generation%20A18%20processor%20is%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20iPhone%2015's%20two-year-old%20A16%20processor.%20But%20in%20day-to-day%20use%2C%20the%20difference%20will%20not%20be%20perceivable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20quick%20performance%20will%20likely%20last%20at%20least%20a%20year%20longer%20than%20the%20iPhone%2015's%20due%20to%20its%20newer%20processor.%20The%20iPhone%2015%20might%20start%20to%20open%20and%20run%20apps%20somewhat%20slower%20in%20about%20three%20years%2C%20whereas%20we%20might%20expect%20slower%20iPhone%2016e%20performance%20in%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsidering%20Apple's%20usual%20seven-year%20support%20window%20for%20the%20iOS%20operating%20system%2C%20we'd%20expect%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20to%20be%20supported%20until%202032.%20The%20iPhone%2015%2C%20released%20in%20September%202023%2C%20will%20likely%20stop%20getting%20support%20in%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20gaming%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20and%20iPhone%2015%20score%20about%20the%20same%20in%20benchmark%20tests.%20They%20also%20play%20games%20as%20well%20as%20each%20other%20at%20similar%20graphics%20settings%20and%20frame%20rates.%20However%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20supports%20AAA%20games%20in%20the%20App%20Store%2C%20as%20well%20as%20ray%20tracing%20(enhanced%20lighting%20effects)%2C%20while%20the%20iPhone%2015%20doesn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b5c041e-fe09-40d4-8cb0-91e7774a680a%5C%22%3EiPhone%2016e%20vs.%20iPhone%2015%3A%20Apple%20Intelligence%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20supports%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20thanks%20to%20its%20A18%20processor.%20The%20iPhone%2015%20doesn't%20support%20Apple%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20on%20a%20wooden%20surface%20shown%20using%20ChatGPT%20processing%20a%20request.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c229e5b1834fe31165dae3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20runs%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%2C%20like%20ChatGPT%20integration%20with%20Siri.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20reason%20to%20rush%20or%20force%20an%20iPhone%20purchase%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20Apple%20Intelligence%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20iPhone%2015%20has%20features%20you%20want%20that%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20doesn't%20have%20%E2%80%94%20namely%2C%20the%20ultrawide%20camera.%20Writing%20Tools%20and%20other%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20aren't%20going%20anywhere%2C%20and%20every%20iPhone%20Apple%20sells%20will%20likely%20support%20Apple%20Intelligence%20in%20a%20year%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20Apple%20Intelligence%20is%20still%20in%20its%20early%20stages%2C%20and%20it's%20continually%20improving%20with%20new%20features%20being%20added%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feature%20that%20will%20most%20likely%20enhance%20your%20iPhone%20experience%20is%20ChatGPT's%20integration%20with%20Siri.%20If%20you've%20previously%20abandoned%20Siri%20for%20getting%20answers%20to%20questions%2C%20the%20ChatGPT%20integration%20with%20Apple%20Intelligence%20will%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20said%2C%20the%20ChatGPT%20app%20is%20available%20on%20any%20iPhone%20that%20runs%20iOS%2017%20or%20later%2C%20so%20you%20can%20run%20it%20on%20the%20iPhone%2015%20with%20a%20similar%20effect%20as%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20with%20Apple%20Intelligence.%20Instead%20of%20using%20Siri%20to%20access%20ChatGPT%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20ChatGPT%20app%20itself%2C%20which%20also%20lets%20you%20use%20your%20voice%20to%20ask%20questions.%20You%20can%20even%20set%20the%20iPhone%2015's%20Action%20button%20as%20a%20shortcut%20for%20ChatGPT%20voice%20functionality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20on%20a%20wooden%20surface%20shown%20processing%20a%20prompt%20