0he's%20perfectly%20willing%20to%20follow%20through%20on%20them.%20But%20they're%20posturing%20until%20they're%20not%20posturing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20having%20his%20staff%20read%20the%20full%20book%2C%20he%20figured%20he'd%20have%20ChatGPT%20summarize%20it.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-bubble-rob-arnott-tech-ai-magnificent-seven-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArnott%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20has%20the%20chatbot%20summarize%20books%20for%20him%20these%20days%20before%20deciding%20whether%20to%20read%20them%20in%20full.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20394-word%20summary%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3ESun%20Tzu's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Art%20of%20War%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20classic%20text%20on%20military%20strategy%20and%20tactics%2C%20written%20around%20the%205th%20century%20BC.%20Despite%20its%20ancient%20origins%2C%20its%20principles%20have%20found%20applications%20in%20various%20fields%20beyond%20the%20military%2C%20including%20business%2C%20sports%2C%20and%20diplomacy.%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20insights%20from%20the%20text%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Importance%20of%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Sun%20Tzu%20emphasizes%20the%20importance%20of%20careful%20planning%20and%20strategy%20over%20reliance%20on%20brute%20force.%20He%20argues%20that%20victory%20can%20be%20achieved%20through%20superior%20strategy%20with%20minimal%20conflict.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20Your%20Enemy%20and%20Yourself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20One%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20quotes%20from%20the%20text%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20know%20the%20enemy%20and%20know%20yourself%2C%20you%20need%20not%20fear%20the%20result%20of%20a%20hundred%20battles%2C%26quot%3B%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20understanding%20both%20your%20own%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%20and%20those%20of%20your%20opponent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20El