ded%2C%20can%20now%20support%20business%20that%20gross%20a%20%26quot%3Bhundred%20million%26quot%3B%20yearly%2C%20while%20still%20being%20run%20by%20small%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20the%20good%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20struggling%20to%20break%20into%20a%20shrinking%20job%20market%2C%20Tan%20says%20the%20advent%20of%20vibe%20coding%20has%20arrived%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20time.%26quot%3B%20It%20gives%20young%20engineers%20the%20opportunity%20to%20strike%20out%20on%20their%20own%20rather%20than%20relying%20on%20big-name%20companies%20to%20kickstart%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20maybe%20it's%20that%20engineer%20who%20couldn't%20get%20a%20job%20at%20Meta%20or%20Google%2C%20who%20actually%20can%20build%20a%20standalone%20business%20making%2010%20or%20100%20million%20dollars%20a%20year%20with%2010%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20said.%20%26quot%3BLike%20that's%20such%20a%20powerful%20moment%20in%20software.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-startups-impact-leaner-garry-tan-y-combinator-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742234884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d854f069253ccddf9973cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-startups-impact-leaner-garry-tan-y-combinator-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Y%20Combinator%20CEO%20Garry%20Tan%20thinks%20%26quot%3Bvibe%20coding%26quot%3B%20is%20set%20to%20transform%20the%20startup%20landscape.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sperkel%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Perkel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-startups-impact-leaner-garry-tan-y-combinator-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Markets%20are%20hopin