0During%20the%2010%20nights%20I%20slept%20on%20it%2C%20I%20didn't%20experience%20neck%20pain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20you%20can't%20add%20or%20remove%20fill%2C%20it%20features%20a%20zipper%20system%20for%20making%20it%20more%20or%20less%20firm.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20softer%20feel%20with%20a%20higher%20loft%2C%20you%20simply%20unzip%20the%20zippers%20along%20the%20lengths%20of%20the%20pillow.%20Zip%20it%20up%20for%20a%20firm%20feel.%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221465%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Brooklinen%20marlow%20pillow%20that%20is%20half%20zipped%20open%20and%20displaying%20some%20of%20the%20interior.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61f8016145edd800183b53c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Brooklinen%20Marlow%20Pillow%20has%20a%20zippable%20gusset%2C%20which%20gives%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20adjustability%20that%20back%20sleepers%20might%20enjoy.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnzipping%20the%20pillow%20reveals%20a%20mesh%20gusset%20that%20lends%20a%20level%20of%20breathability%20to%20the%20Marlow.%20I%20preferred%20the%20softer%2C%20cooler%20feel%20and%20added%20loft%20of%20the%20unzipped%20pillow.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Marlow%20comes%20with%20the%20longest%20risk-free%20trial%20of%20any%20pillows%20we%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20negative%20is%20that%20the%20pillow%20doesn't%20have%20a%20removable%20cover%20and%20is%20spot%20clean%20only.%20You%20may%20want%20to%20spring%20for%20a%20pillowcase%20protector%20to%20help%20it%20last%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a1d0606-20c2-4030-beaa-3d70fc070e69%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20neck%20and%20back%20pain%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20neck%20and%20back%20pain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Coop%20Sleep%20Goods%20Original%20Pillow%20has%20much%20in%20common%2