't%20right%20for%20you.%20We%20only%20recommend%20purchasing%20from%20a%20brand%20that%20still%20allows%20you%20to%20return%20the%20product%20even%20after%20sleeping%20on%20it%20for%20several%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECertiPUR-US%20certification%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20is%20a%20standard%20for%20polyurethane%20foams%2C%20including%20memory%20foam.%20Pillows%20that%20are%20CertiPUR-US%20certified%20are%20made%20without%20heavy%20metals%2C%20flame%20retardants%2C%20ozone%20depleters%2C%20phthalates%2C%20and%20formaldehyde.%20They%20also%20have%20low%20VOC%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285785132-0140-4f91-a308-f489905d8c19%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20pillows%20for%20neck%20pain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stuffing%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20eli%20and%20elm%20side%20sleeper%20cotton%20pillow%2C%20sitting%20on%20a%20wooden%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61f801fe415c3f0018d3aef8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20personally%20tested%20every%20pillow%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20and%20also%20sent%20additional%20pillows%20to%20Insider%20staffers%20that%20suffer%20from%20neck%20pain%20to%20validate%20my%20findings.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20each%20of%20the%20pillows%20in%20this%20guide%20through%20several%20tests%2C%20including%20sleeping%20on%20each%20for%20at%20least%20three%20nights.%20When%20shopping%20for%20a%20pillow%2C%20the%20most%20important%20factors%20to%20consider%20are%20comfort%2C%20return%20policy%2C%20and%20adjustability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20main%20attributes%20we%20look%20for%20and%20how%20we%20test%20them%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20tested%20each%20of%20the%20pillows%20for%20at%20least%20three%20nights.%20For%20reference%2C%20I'm%206%20feet%20tall%20and%20215%20pounds.%20I%20mainly%20sleep%20on%20my%20side%20but%20can%20find%20comfort%20in%20any%20position.%20Each%20morning%2C%20I%20would%20record%20how%20comfortable%20I%20felt%20on%20the%20pillow%2C%20if%20I%20experienced%20any%20neck%20pain%2C%20and%20how%20well%20I%20slept.%20Since%20several%20factors%20play%20into%20pillow%20comfort%2C%20including%20your%20body%20type%20and%20sleeping%20style%2C%20the%20firmness%20of%20your%20bed%2C%20personal%20preferences%20and%20more%2C%20I%20also%20enlisted%20the%20help%20of%20six%20neck-pain%20sufferers%20on%20the%20Insider%20Reviews%20team%20to%20help%20me%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturn%20policy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20only%20way%20to%20find%20out%20if%20a%20pillow%20is%20truly%20right%20for%20you%20is%20to%20sleep%20on%20it%20for%20several%20nights.%20We%20gave%20preference%20to%20pillows%20that%20had%20a%20trial%20period%20of%20at%20least%2060%20days%20and%20a%20return%20policy%20free%20of%20loopholes%2C%20like%20requiring%20the%20customer%20pay%20return%20shipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdjustability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdjustable%20pillows%20are%20great%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20hassle%20of%20returning%20a%20pillow%20or%20if%20your%20comfort%20preferences%20change%20over%20time.%20An%20adjustable%20pillow%20will%20help%20ensure%20your%20neck%20gets%20the%20precise%20support%20you%20need.%20Pillows%20with%20loose%20fill%20that%20you%20can%20add%20or%20remove%20scored%20higher%20in%20our%20testing%20since%20they%20allow%20you%20to%20achieve%20a%20more-precise%20customization.%20Models%20with%20inserts%20were%20less%20helpful%20since%20customization%20was%20limited.%20Pillows%20that%20weren't%20adjustable%20at%20all%20lost%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20cleaned%20all%20of%20the%20pillows%20according%20to%20the%20manufacturers'%20directions.%20Many%20had%20removable%20machine-washable%20covers.%20A%20few%2C%20including%20the%20MyPillow%20pillows%2C%20were%20entirely%20machine-washable.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20gauge%20when%20they%20were%20completely%20dry.%20I%20rated%20each%20pillow%20on%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20clean%20and%20how%20cleaning%20impacted%20the%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22698e3a89-300d-4fa3-bbea-9335e65159bf%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ENeck%20pain%20pillow%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20a%20pillow%20cause%20neck%20pain%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20If%20a%20pillow%20has%20too%20much%20loft%2C%20your%20head%20will%20bend%20forward%20too%20much%20when%20sleeping%20on%20your%20back%2C%20overstretching%20the%20back%20of%20your%20neck.%20If%20there's%20too%20little%20loft%2C%20your%20head%20tilts%20back%20and%20overstretches%20the%20front%20of%20your%20neck.%20You%20want%20to%20keep%20your%20neck%20in%20a%20neutral%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20should%20I%20sleep%20to%20avoid%20neck%20pain%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EColleen%20Louw%2C%20a%20physical%20therapist%20and%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apta.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Physical%20Therapy%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20discourages%20people%20from%20sleeping%20on%20their%20stomaches%20because%20sleeping%20with%20your%20head%20turned%20can%20lead%20to%20neck%20pain.%20Instead%2C%20sleep%20on%20your%20back%20or%20side%20with%20your%20spine%20aligned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Layla%20Kapok%20Pillow%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Layla%20kapok%20pillow%20set%20on%20a%20wood%20table%20with%20some%20filling%20exposed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61f80072415c3f0018d3ae5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Layla%20Kapok%20Pillow%20features%20an%20adjustable%20fill%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20a%20great%20pick%20for%20sleepers%20of%20all%20styles.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAll%20sleeping%20styles%2C%20especially%20side%20sleepers%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAvailable%20sizes%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EQueen%20(18%26quot%3B%20x%2028%26quot%3B)%20and%20king%20(18%26quot%3B%20x%2034%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFill%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECertiPUR-US%20certified%20shredded%20memory%20foam%20and%20Kapok%20fibers%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirmness%20(1%20softest%20to%2010%20firmest)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E4%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHypoallergenic%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECare%20instructions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERemove%20fill%2C%20machine%20wash%20cover%20cold%2C%20tumble%20dry%20low.%20Do%20not%20iron.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrial%20period%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E120%20nights%20(free%20returns)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E5%20years%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERemovable%20fill%20for%20precise%20customization%2C%20incredibly%20comfortable%20and%20moldable%20to%20cradle%20your%20neck%2Fhead%2C%20made%20with%20CertiPUR-US%20certified%20foam%2C%20easy-to-clean%20cover%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERemoving%20the%20fill%20can%20get%20messy%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Layla%20Kapok%20Pillow%20was%20the%20best%20pillow%20we%20tested%20by%20far.%20It's%20filled%20with%20CertiPUR-US%20certified%20shredded%20memory%20foam%20and%20fibers%20from%20the%20Kapok%20tree.%20The%20fibers%20are%20light%2C%20buoyant%2C%20and%20commonly%20used%20as%20a%20down%20alternative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20adjust%20the%20pillow%2C%20you%20unzip%20the%20machine-washable%20cover%20and%20internal%20case%20and%20remove%20as%20much%20fill%20as%20you%20need%20to%20achieve%20your%20preferred%20loft.%20You'll%20want%20to%20remove%20a%20little%20fill%20at%20a%20time%3B%20otherwise%2C%20you%20may%20end%20up%20with%20shreds%20of%20fill%20all%20over%20your%20bedroom.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20switched%20to%20the%20Layla%20pillow%20when%20I%20awoke%20with%20neck%20pain%2C%20and%20it%20did%20a%20great%20job%20of%20assuaging%20the%20pain.%20The%20loft%20was%20exactly%20what%20I%20needed%20for%20side%20sleeping%20without%20removing%20any%20fill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2C%20executive%20editor%20for%20Insider%20Reviews%20and%20a%20more%20petite%20side%20sleeper%20than%20me%2C%20also%20tested%20the%20Layla%20Kapok%20and%20loved%20it.%20She%20prefers%20flat%20and%20moldable%20pillows%2C%20so%20she%20removed%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20fill.%20This%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20manipulate%20the%20remaining%20fill%20to%20support%20her%20head%20and%20neck.%20Kaplan%20said%20it%20took%20a%20couple%20of%20nights%20to%20get%20the%20adjustments%20just%20right%2C%20but%20once%20it%20was%20there%2C%20she%20slept%20much%20better%20than%20with%20her%20old%20memory%20foam%20pillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20side%20sleepers%3A%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20Cotton%20Side%20Sleeper%20Pillow%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221462%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Eli%20and%20elm%20cotton%20pillow%20on%20a%20tabletop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61f800ff415c3f0018d3ae83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221097%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20unique%20shape%20of%20the%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20Cotton%20Side%20Sleeper%20Pillow%20provides%20C-shaped%20support%2C%20which%20is%20helpful%20for%20those%20that%20sleep%20on%20their%20sides.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESide%20sleepers%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAvailable%20sizes%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E17%26quot%3B%20x%2029%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFill%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELatex%20and%20polyester%20fiber%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirmness%20(1%20softest%20to%2010%20firmest)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E5%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHypoallergenic%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECare%20instructions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERemove%20cover%2C%20machine%20wash%20cover%20cold%20water%2C%20tumble%20dry%20low%2C%20do%20not%20bleach%2C%20do%20not%20use%20fabric%20softener%2C%20iron%20on%20low.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrial%20period%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E45%20days%20(free%20returns)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E5%20years%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EMachine-washable%20cover%2C%20precise%20adjustability%2C%20comfortable%20for%20all%20types%20of%20sleepers%2C%20particularly%20side%20sleepers%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ERemoving%20the%20fill%20can%20get%20messy%2C%20home-trial%20period%20is%20relatively%20short%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20Cotton%20Side%20Sleeper%20Pillow%20and%20our%20top%20pick%20were%20the%20only%20two%20pillows%20in%20our%20tests%20deemed%20comfortable%20by%20multiple%20testers%20with%20neck%20pain.%20Your%20neck%20and%20shoulder%20stay%20supported%20thanks%20to%20the%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20pillow's%20U%20shape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20pillow%20is%20filled%20with%20latex%20and%20polyester%20that%20you%20can%20remove%20to%20customize%20the%20feel.%20We%20suggest%20taking%20out%20a%20little%20fill%20at%20a%20time%20to%20avoid%20a%20mess.%20Despite%20its%20shape%2C%20the%20pillow%20fits%20a%20standard%20pillowcase%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-52949-20%26h%3Daf3cd7f92c759c37d1562e030060b0e7f2ba1d3b5b963d7c70785b0316fa9524%26postID%3D61eb1e8c9d8132253b1be1a7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-pillow-for-neck-pain%26