d%20be%20supportive%20and%20the%20right%20firmness%20for%20your%20sleep%20style.%20We%20like%20adjustable%20pillows%20because%20you%20can%20customize%20the%20fill%20to%20fit%20your%20body.%20The%20right%20loft%20is%20achieved%20when%20your%20head%20and%20neck%20aligned%20with%20your%20spine%20in%20your%20preferred%20sleeping%20position.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Consider%20a%20material%20that's%20supportive%20yet%20adaptable.%20In%20general%2C%20we%20recommend%20opting%20for%20pillows%20made%20of%20synthetic%20materials%2C%20like%20foam%20or%20polyester.%20Bedding%20filled%20with%20down%20or%20other%20animal%20products%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20cause%20an%20allergic%20reaction.%20Currently%2C%20there%20is%20no%20certification%20process%20that%20a%20manufacturer%20must%20go%20through%20in%20order%20to%20call%20its%20pillows%20hypoallergenic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturn%20policy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20good%20return%20policy%20is%20vital%20if%20the%20pillow%20isn't%20right%20for%20you.%20We%20only%20recommend%20purchasing%20from%20a%20brand%20that%20still%20allows%20you%20to%20return%20the%20product%20even%20after%20sleeping%20on%20it%20for%20several%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECertiPUR-US%20certification%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20is%20a%20standard%20for%20polyurethane%20foams%2C%20including%20memory%20foam.%20Pillows%20that%20are%20CertiPUR-US%20certified%20are%20made%20without%20heavy%20metals%2C%20flame%20retardants%2C%20ozone%20depleters%2C%20phthalates%2C%20and%20formaldehyde.%20They%20also%20have%20low%20VOC%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20test%20neck%20pain%20pillows%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stuffing%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20eli%20and%20elm%20side%20sleeper%20cotton%20pillow%2C%20sitting%20on%20a%20wooden%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61f801fe415c3f0018d3aef8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20personally%20tested%20every%20pillow%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20and%20also%20sent%20additional%20pillows%20to%20Insider%20staffers%20that%20suffer%20from%20neck%20pain%20to%20validate%20my%20findings.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20each%20of%20the%20pillows%20in%20this%20guide%20through%20several%20tests%2C%20including%20sleeping%20on%20each%20for%20at%20least%20three%20nights.%20When%20shopping%20for%20a%20pillow%2C%20the%20most%20important%20factors%20to%20consider%20are%20comfort%2C%20return%20policy%2C%20and%20adjustability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20main%20attributes%20we%20look%20for%20and%20how%20we%20test%20them%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20tested%20each%20of%20the%20pillows%20for%20at%20least%20three%20nights.%20For%20reference%2C%20I'm%206%20feet%20tall%20and%20215%20pounds.%20I%20mainly%20sleep%20on%20my%20side%20but%20can%20find%20comfort%20in%20any%20position.%20Each%20morning%2C%20I%20would%20record%20how%20comfortable%20I%20felt%20on%20the%20pillow%2C%20if%20I%20experienced%20any%20neck%20pain%2C%20and%20how%20well%20I%20slept.%20Since%20several%20factors%20play%20into%20pillow%20comfort%2C%20including%20your%20body%20type%20and%20sleeping%20style%2C%20the%20firmness%20of%20your%20bed%2C%20personal%20preferences%20and%20more%2C%20I%20also%20enlisted%20the%20help%20of%20six%20neck-pain%20sufferers%20on%20the%20Insider%20Reviews%20team%20to%20help%20me%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturn%20policy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20only%20way%20to%20find%20out%20if%20a%20pillow%20is%20truly%20right%20for%20you%20is%20to%20sleep%20on%20it%20for%20several%20nights.%20We%20gave%20preference%20to%20pillows%20that%20had%20a%20trial%20period%20of%20at%20least%2060%20days%20and%20a%20return%20policy%20free%20of%20loopholes%2C%20like%20requiring%20the%20customer%20pay%20return%20shipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdjustability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdjustable%20pillows%20are%20great%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20hassle%20of%20returning%20a%20pillow%20or%20if%20your%20comfort%20preferences%20change%20over%20time.%20An%20adjustable%20pillow%20will%20help%20ensure%20your%20neck%20gets%20the%20precise%20support%20you%20need.%20Pillows%20with%20loose%20fill%20that%20you%20can%20add%20or%20remove%20scored%20higher%20in%20our%20testing%20since%20they%20allow%20you%20to%20achieve%20a%20more-precise%20customization.%20Models%20with%20inserts%20were%20less%20helpful%20since%20customization%20was%20limited.%20Pillows%20that%20weren't%20adjustable%20at%20all%20lost%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20cleaned%20all%20of%20the%20pillows%20according%20to%20the%20manufacturers'%20directions.%20Many%20had%20removable%20machine-washable%20covers.%20A%20few%2C%20including%20the%20MyPillow%20pillows%2C%20were%20entirely%20machine-washable.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20gauge%20when%20they%20were%20completely%20dry.%20I%20rated%20each%20pillow%20on%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20clean%20and%20how%20cleaning%20impacted%20the%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENeck%20pain%20pillow%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cat%20laying%20on%20top%20of%20a%20pile%20of%20pillows.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61eb26bdd265300018043b3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20cat%20was%20particularly%20appreciative%20of%20me%20testing%2017%20pillows%20for%20this%20guide.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20a%20pillow%20cause%20neck%20pain%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20If%20a%20pillow%20has%20too%20much%20loft%2C%20your%20head%20will%20bend%20forward%20too%20much%20when%20sleeping%20on%20your%20back%2C%20overstretching%20the%20back%20of%20your%20neck.%20If%20there's%20too%20little%20loft%2C%20your%20head%20tilts%20back%20and%20overstretches%20the%20front%20of%20your%20neck.%20You%20want%20to%20keep%20your%20neck%20in%20a%20neutral%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20should%20I%20sleep%20to%20avoid%20neck%20pain%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EColleen%20Louw%2C%20a%20physical%20therapist%20and%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apta.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Physical%20Therapy%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20discourages%20people%20from%20stomach%20sleeping%20because%20they%20have%20to%20sleep%20with%20their%20heads%20turned%2C%20leading%20to%20neck%20pain.%20Instead%2C%20sleep%20on%20your%20back%20or%20side%20with%20your%20spine%20aligned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillow-for-neck-pain%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742234461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61eb26ba2b43ff00185e1dd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillow-for-neck-pain%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20pillows%20for%20neck%20pain%20support%20the%20spine%20and%20reduce%20tension%20to%20curb%20aches%20and%20pains.%20We%20tested%20options%20for%20side%2C%20back%2C%20and%20stomach%20sleepers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jbrains%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Brains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillow-for-neck-pain%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20couple%20detained%20by%20Taliban%20'moved%20to%20maximum%20security%20prison'%20as%20family%20raise%20health%20fears%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742234400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F02