ks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20India%20and%20New%20Zealand%20%26quot%3Bwill%20continue%20to%20cooperate%20together%20against%20terrorist%2C%20separatist%2C%20and%20radical%20elements%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20context%2C%20we%20shared%20our%20concern%20about%20anti-India%20activities%20by%20some%20illegal%20elements%20in%20New%20Zealand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20confident%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20receive%20cooperation%20from%20the%20New%20Zealand%20government%20against%20all%20these%20illegal%20elements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20also%20said%20that%20both%20sides%20have%20agreed%20to%20strengthen%20and%20institutionalise%20their%20defence%20and%20security%20partnership%2C%20and%20a%20roadmap%20will%20be%20prepared%20for%20cooperation%20in%20the%20defence%20industry%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20defence%20and%20security%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20said%20that%20India%20and%20New%20Zealand%20have%20decided%20to%20start%20negotiations%20for%20a%20mutually%20beneficial%20free%20trade%20pact.%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20boost%20the%20potential%20of%20mutual%20trade%20and%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BMutual%20cooperation%20and%20investment%20will%20be%20encouraged%20in%20areas%20like%20dairy%2C%20food%20processing%2C%20and%20pharma.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20also%20discussed%20about%20a%20new%20arrangement%20between%20India%20and%20New%20Zealand%20to%20facilitate%20the%20mobility%20of%20professionals%20and%20skilled%20workers.%20The%20proposed%20arrangement%20on%20skilled%20workforce%20mobility%20will%20facilitate%20the%20movement%20of%20professionals%2C%20fostering%20stronger%20people-to-people%20ties%2C%20and%20economic%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand%20also%20formally%20joined%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20Oceans'%20Initiative%20(IPOI)%20and%20became%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Coalition%20for%20Disaster%20Resilient%20Infrastructure%20(CDRI)%2C%20marking%20its%20deeper%20engagement%20in%20regional%20and%20global%20frameworks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20pact%20signed%20by%20both%20countries%20is%20the%20Authorised%20Economic%20Operator%20-%20Mutual%20Recognition%20Agreement%20or%20AEO-MRA.%20The%20agreement%20is%20aimed%20at%20streamlining%20trade%20processes%20and%20enhancing%20customs%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20a%20Memorandum%20of%20Cooperation%20on%20Horticulture%20was%20signed%20between%20India's%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers'%20Welfare%20and%20New%20Zealand's%20Ministry%20for%20Primary%20Industries.%20A%20Letter%20of%20Intent%20on%20Forestry%20was%20also%20exchanged%20between%20India's%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%2C%20and%20Climate%20Change%20and%20its%20New%20Zealand%20counterpart%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20deepening%20collaboration%2C%20an%20Education%20Cooperation%20Agreement%20was%20signed%20between%20both%20nations'%20education%20ministries%2C%20along%20with%20a%20Memorandum%20of%20Cooperation%20in%20Sports%20between%20India's%20Ministry%20of%20Youth%20Affairs%20%26amp%3B%20Sports%20and%20Sport%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3E(Inputs%20from%20PTI%20and%20ANI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742232420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F5i0n09ds_narendra-modi-nz-pm-christopher-luxon-ani_625x300_17_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-new-zealand-ink-defence-pact-hold-talks-on-free-trade-agreement-7946225%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20counterpart%20from%20New%20Zealand%20Christopher%20Luxon%20held%20wide-ranging%20bilateral%20talks%20in%20New%20Delhi%20today%2C%20following%20which%20the%20two%20nations%20