.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governments%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%20and%20some%20private%20entities%20have%20used%20her%20photograph%20from%20the%20website%20without%20her%20consent%20for%20their%20advertisements%20and%20hoardings%2C%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20further%20said%20that%20the%20government's%20illegal%20use%20of%20her%20photograph%20was%20a%20breach%20of%20her%20fundamental%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20sought%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20respondents%20to%20be%20permanently%20restrained%20from%20using%20her%20photograph%20on%20their%20websites%2C%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20advertisements%20and%20promotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742218920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Frmvo6quo_bombay-high-court_625x300_27_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbombay-high-court-on-use-of-womans-pic-in-government-ads-commercial-exploitation-7943233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20termed%20the%20use%20of%20a%20woman's%20image%20without%20her%20consent%20in%20government%20advertisements%20as%20%26quot%3Bcommercial%20exploitation%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bquite%20serious%26quot%3B%20considering%20the%20contemporary%20electronic%20era%20and%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbombay-high-court-on-use-of-womans-pic-in-government-ads-commercial-exploitation-7943233%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ericsson%2C%20Airtel%2C%20Volvo%20partner%20to%20research%205G%20digital%20twin%20tech%2C%20AI%22%2C%22content%2