expected%20to%20be%20released%20this%20evening%20or%20tomorrow%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Revathi%20-%20the%20Managing%20Director%20of%20online%20news%20channel%20Pulse%20News%20-%20and%20Ms%20Yadav%20-%20a%20reporter%20with%20the%20channel%20were%20arrested%20last%20week%20by%20police%20officers%20in%20plain%20clothes%20over%20a%20widely-circulated%20video%20on%20X.%20The%20complaint%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20State%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Congress%20Social%20Media%20Cell%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20a%20Hyderabad%20court%20dropped%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-setback-for-revanth-reddy-court-drops-key-charge-of-organised-crime-against-2-journalists-7942069%5C%22%3E%20'organised%20crime'%20charge%20against%20the%20two%20journalists%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20court%20said%20that%20the%20case%20was%20not%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Borganised%20crime%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20were%20no%20%26quot%3Bmonetary%20transactions%20made%26quot%3B%20so%20the%20charge%20doesn't%20apply%20to%20the%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20court%20maintained%20other%20charges%20under%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20and%20BNS%20provisions%20related%20to%20creating%20and%20circulating%20false%20information%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20FIR%20prima%20facie%20contained%20well-founded%20accusations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Video%20In%20The%20Eye%20Of%20The%20Storm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20erupted%20after%20a%20video%20where%20Ms%20Yadav%20was%20seen%20interviewing%20a%20man%20who%20was%20allegedly%20heard%20using%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20the%20Congress%20government%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20went%20viral.%20Ms%20Revathy%20allegedly%20posted%20the%20video%20on%20her%20social%20media%20page%20which%20then%20got%20amplified.%20The%20police%20suspect%20the%20video%20has%20been%20shot%20inside%20the%20BRS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20video%20was%20shot%20in%20February%20but%20started%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20on%20March%2010%2C%20allegedly%20to%20coincide%20with%20the%20Budget%20session%20of%20the%20Telangana%20Legislative%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budget%20session%20of%20the%20Telangana%20assembly%20began%20on%20March%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20also%20said%20that%20they%20would%20be%20looking%20into%20the%20funding%20of%20the%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevanth%20Reddy's%20Warning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20taken%20a%20strong%20stance%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20warning%20that%20stringent%20action%20would%20be%20taken%2C%20as%20per%20the%20law%2C%20against%20those%20engaging%20in%20%26quot%3Bdefamatory%20propaganda%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20journalism.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20leaders%20of%20journalists'%20unions%20should%20define%20a%20journalist%20and%20a%20list%20of%20(mainstream)%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%2C%20said%20his%20%26quot%3Bblood%20is%20boiling%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20remarks%20and%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20have%20the%20people%20who%20posted%20these%20marked%20%26quot%3Bstripped%20and%20paraded%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20in%20the%20same%20breadth%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20exceed%20any%20limits%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20the%20opposition%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20for%20defending%20the%20journalists%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BRS%20is%20upset%20when%20police%20cases%20are%20filed%20against%20paid%20artistes%20who%20posted%20abusive%20videos%20recorded%20in%20their%20party%20office%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBRS%20working%20president%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20met%20the%20two%20women%20at%20the%20Chanchalguda%20jail%20this%20afternoon.%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20leader%20said%20the%20arrest%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bviolation%20of%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20wrong%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20police%20to%20arrest%20the%20journalists%20in%20such%20a%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKT%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20NDTV's%20Uma%20Sudhir%2C%20criticised%20the%20police%20action%2C%20saying%20it%20%26quot%3Breminding%20us%20of%20emergency%20days%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20asked%20if%20the%20channel%20was%20funded%20by%20BRS%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20does%20it%20matter%3F%20People%20can%20still%20post%20and%20say%20whatever%20they%20want%20to%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20court%20issued%20a%20show-cause%20notice%20to%20the%20investigative%20officer%20of%20the%20case%2C%20seeking%20answers%20on%20how%20a%20police%20team%20went%20to%20the%20homes%20of%20the%20journalists%20in%20plain%20clothes%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20why%20their%20families%20weren't%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742215200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fnhchjqk_journo_625x300_17_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2F2-women-journalists-pogadadanda-revathi-thanvi-yadav-arrested-for-post-against-revanth-reddy-get-bail-7944068%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20women%20journalists%20who%20were%20arrested%20earlier%20this%20month%20for%20allegedly%20circulating%20%26quot%3Babusive%26quot%3B%20content%20against%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20have%20secured%20bail%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2F2-women-journalists-pogadadanda-revathi-thanvi-yadav-arrested-for-post-against-revanth-reddy-get-bail-7944068%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20An%20Anonymous%20Letter%20Exposed%20UP%20Teacher's%20Abuse%20Of%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPolice%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Hathras%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20suspended%20Chief%20Proctor%20of%20a%20college%2C%20who%20faces%20serious%20allegations%20of%20sexually%20abusing%20students%20and%20recording%20the%20acts%20to%20blackmail%20them.%20Rajnish%20Kumar%20is%20Chief%20Proctor%20of%20Seth%20Phool%20Chand%20Bagla%20PG%20College%2C%20also%20known%20as%20'Old%20Degree%20College'.%20The%20college%20administration%20suspended%20him%20after%20the%20allegations%20came%20to%20the%20fore.%20Kumar%20is%20now%20on%20the%20run%20and%20police%20are%20looking%20for%20him.%20Disturbing%20images%20of%20him%20sexually%20assaulting%20students%20of%20the%20college%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20intensifying%20calls%20for%20strict%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Anonymous%20Letter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2010%20months%20back%2C%20police%20received%20an%20anonymous%20letter%2C%20accusing%20Kumar%20of%20blackmailing%20students%20into%20sexual%20acts%20in%20return%20for%20passing%20marks%20and%20teaching%20job%20opportunities.%20Recently%2C%20NDTV%2C%20too%2C%20received%20an%20anonymous%20letter%2C%20in%20which%20the%20writer%20said%20she%20had%20written%20to%20all%20authorities%20and%20sought%20help%2C%20but%20got%20no%20response.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20used%20my%20real%20name%20because%20then%20this%20ruthless%20professor%20will%20kill%20me.%20But%20what%20I%20cannot%20understand%20is%20don't%20the%20pictures%20I%20enclosed%20prove%20his%20crime%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Pendrive%2C%20And%2059%20Obscene%20Videos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnclosed%20with%20the%20anonymous%20complaints%20is%20a%20pen%20drive%20with%2059%20videos%20of%20Kumar%20getting%20intimate%20with%20students.%20The%20students'%20faces%20have%20been%20concealed%20to%20protect%20their%20identities.%20Kumar%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20would%20record%20the%20acts%20with%20a%20hidden%20camera%20and%20later%20blackmail%20the%20victims%20into%20getting%20intimate%20again.%20In%20her%20letter%20to%20NDTV%2C%20the%20complainant%20has%20alleged%20that%20Kumar%20has%20targeted%20numerous%20women%20and%20that%20the%20others%20in%20the%20college%20administration%20are%20hand-in-glove%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Action%20So%20Far%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20Kumar%2C%20charging%20him%20under%20sections%20related%20to%20rape%2C%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20sexual%20intercourse%20by%20a%20person%20in%20authority.%20Shortly%20after%20the%20police%20filed%20the%20case%2C%20Kumar%20was%20suspended%20as%20the%20Chief%20Proctor.%20According%20to%20a%20PTI%20report%2C%20the%20accused%20said%20he%20had%20been%20facing%20such%20allegations%20for%2018%20months%20and%20that%20several%20probes%20had%20not%20yielded%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20Challenge%20For%20Cops%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20a%20key%20challenge%20in%20their%20investigation%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20recorded%20statement%20by%20the%20complainant.%20The%20videos%2C%20they%20said%2C%20date%20back%20to%202023.%20The%20complainant%2C%20however%2C%20has%20stressed%20that%20she%20is%20scared%20to%20reveal%20her%20identity.%20She%20has%20also%20said%20no%20student%20allegedly%20assaulted%20by%20Kumar%20would%20come%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20fearing%20stigma%20and%20further%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742215020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F7our6ftg_hathras_625x300_17_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnish-sharma-hathras-how-an-anonymous-letter-exposed-up-teachers-chilling-abuse-of-students-7943478%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Hathras%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20suspended%20Chief%20Proctor%20of%20a%20college%2C%20who%20faces%20serious%20allegations%20of%20sexually%20abusing%20students%