tainty%20As%20Trump%20Declares%20Presidential%20Pardons%20%26quot%3BNull%2C%20Void%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20faces%20uncertainty%20after%20his%20successor%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20declared%20that%20Biden's%20last-minute%20presidential%20pardons%2C%20including%20one%20to%20his%20son%20Hunter%20Biden%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Bnull%20and%20void%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20said%20that%20Joe%20Biden%20may%20not%20even%20have%20been%20aware%20of%20what%20all%20was%20being%20signed%20in%20his%20name%20as%20an%20autopen%20was%20used%20to%20sign%20these%20documents.%20President%20Trump%20made%20this%20announcement%20on%20his%20social%20media%20platform%20Truth%20Social%20late%20on%20Sunday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20autopen%20is%20a%20robotic%20instrument%20that%20is%20used%20by%20government%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20US%20President%2C%20to%20sign%20documents%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20said%20authority%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20sheer%20volumes%20of%20correspondence%20they%20have%20to%20sign.%20Such%20signatures%20are%20usually%20communicated%20to%20the%20person%20in-charge%20as%20they%20need%20not%20necessarily%20be%20aware%20of%20such%20signatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Presidents%20have%20used%20the%20autopen%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20'pardons'%20that%20Sleepy%20Joe%20Biden%20gave%20to%20the%20Unselect%20Committee%20of%20political%20thugs%2C%20and%20many%20others%2C%20are%20hereby%20declared%20void%2C%20vacant%2C%20and%20of%20no%20further%20force%20or%20effect%2C%20because%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20were%20done%20by%20autopen.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20Joe%20Biden%20did%20not%20sign%20them%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20he%20did%20not%20know%20anything%20about%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Trump%20stated.%20He%20however%2C%20did%20not%20give%20any%20proof%20of%20this%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20all%20such%20people%20who%20were%20falsely%20%26quot%3Bpardoned%26quot%3B%20by%20Biden%20just%20before%20he%20demitted%20office%20will%20now%20face%20investigation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20necessary%20Pardoning%20Documents%20were%20not%20explained%20to%2C%20or%20approved%20by%2C%20Biden.%20He%20knew%20nothing%20about%20them%2C%20and%20the%20people%20that%20did%20may%20have%20committed%20a%20crime.%20Therefore%2C%20those%20on%20the%20Unselect%20Committee%2C%20who%20destroyed%20and%20deleted%20ALL%20evidence%20obtained%20during%20their%20two%20year%20Witch%20Hunt%20of%20me%2C%20and%20many%20other%20innocent%20people%2C%20should%20fully%20understand%20that%20they%20are%20subject%20to%20investigation%20at%20the%20highest%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcluding%20his%20post%2C%20President%20Trump%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20is%2C%20they%20were%20probably%20responsible%20for%20the%20Documents%20that%20were%20signed%20on%20their%20behalf%20without%20the%20knowledge%20or%20consent%20of%20the%20Worst%20President%20in%20the%20History%20of%20our%20Country%2C%20Crooked%20Joe%20Biden!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F114175908922736427%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presidential%20pardon%20is%20an%20absolute%20power%20that%20all%20US%20Presidents%20have.%20Even%20the%20courts%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20cannot%20intervene%20in%20such%20a%20matter.%20In%20the%20past%20courts%20have%20been%20opposed%20to%20putting%20any%20limits%20or%20restrictions%20on%20how%20these%20pardons%20are%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20Donald%20Trump%20convert%20his%20statement%20into%20a%20presidential%20order%2C%20it%20would%20mean%20that%20the%20investigation%20agencies%20will%20probe%20those%20who%20were%20%26quot%3Bpardoned%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%20may%20potentially%20go%20after%20and%20prosecute%20some%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20arch%20rivals%20and%20political%20adversaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20however%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20board%20the%20Air%20Force%20One%20late%20on%20Sunday%20night%20that%20ultimately%20the%20courts%20should%20decide%20on%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20pardons.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20my%20decision.%20That%20will%20ultimately%20be%20up%20to%20a%20court.%20But%20I%20would%20say%20that%20they%20(Biden's%20last-minute%20pardons)%20are%20null%20and%20void%2C%20because%20I'm%20sure%20Biden%20didn't%20have%20any%20idea%20that%20it%20was%20taking%20place%2C%20and%20somebody%20was%20using%20an%20autopen%20to%20sign%20off%20and%20to%20give%20these%20pardons%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Trump%20said%2C%20alleging%20that%20these%20were%20forged%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20ruling%20in%202024%2C%20a%20US%20federal%20appeals%20court%20had%20noted%20that%20a%20presidential%20pardon%20doesn't%20necessarily%20have%20to%20be%20in%20writing.%20%26quot%3BThe%20plain%20language%20of%20the%20US%20Constitution%20imposes%20no%20such%20limit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20presidential%20pardon%20has%20been%20an%20absolute%20power%20of%20all%20US%20Presidents%20for%20more%20than%20a%20century%20now.%20So%20far%20they%20have%20never%20been%20challenged%2C%20but%20Donald%20Trump's%20move%20on%20Sunday%20night%20may%20lead%20to%20an%20attempt%20to%20upend%20such%20tradition.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742212380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fukprdv0o_trump-biden_625x300_21_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-in-trouble-as-donald-trump-declares-his-presidential-pardons-null-and-void-7943568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20faces%20uncertainty%20after%20his%20successor%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20declared%20t