%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKifayatullah%20Malik%20is%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20prestigious%20President%E2%80%99s%20Award%20for%20National%20Social%20Service%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20ambitions%20do%20not%20stop%20here.%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20mission%20is%20to%20bridge%20the%20digital%20literacy%20gap%20and%20ensure%20basic%20education%20for%20all%20tribal%20children%20who%20left%20their%20education%20midway%20because%20of%20poverty.%20He%20plans%20to%20expand%20his%20efforts%20beyond%20North%20Kashmir%20and%20sustain%20his%20initiatives%20through%20NGO%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20child%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20they%20come%20from%2C%20deserves%20a%20chance%20to%20learn.%20I%20will%20keep%20working%20until%20every%20tribal%20child%20has%20access%20to%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20dedication%20has%20earned%20him%20several%20prestigious%20accolades%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20President%E2%80%99s%20Award%20for%20National%20Social%20Service%20(NSS)%20(2021-22)%E2%80%94the%20first-ever%20recipient%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Best%20Forest%20Friend%20Award%20by%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Social%20Forestry%20Department%20for%20his%20large-scale%20tree-planting%20initiatives.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Ambassador%20of%20Humanity%20Award%20(2024).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Global%20Human%20Rights%20Award.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20honours%20underscore%20his%20far-reaching%20impact%E2%80%94not%20just%20in%20education%20but%20also%20in%20environmental%20conservation%20and%20humanitarian%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Malik%2C%20the%20journey%20is%20far%20from%20over.%20He%20continues%20to%20work%20tirelessly%2C%20ensuring%20that%20no%20child%20in%20his%20community%20is%20denied%20the%20right%20to%20education.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20change%20one%20life%2C%20you%20create%20a%20ripple%20effect.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20re-enrolling%20students.%20Tomorrow%2C%20they%20will%20be%20the%20ones%20advocating%20for%20education%20in%20their%20own%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20vision%20and%20persistence%2C%20Malik%20is%20proving%20that%20grassroots%20efforts%20can%20drive%20meaningful%20change.%20In%20the%20remote%20villages%20of%20North%20Kashmir%2C%20where%20access%20to%20education%20was%20once%20uncertain%2C%20opportunities%20are%20now%20being%20reclaimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Tauseef%20Ahmad%20and%20Sajid%20Raina%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742182201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fmalik_kifayatullah-20250301-0007-1_11zon-1742181901.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D413762%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kifayatullah%20Malik%20knows%20the%20pain%20of%20nearly%20losing%20his%20education.%20Now%2C%20at%2025%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20helping%20tribal%20children%20overcome%20the%20same%20struggles%20%E2%80%94%20ensuring%20they%20stay%20in%20school%20despite%20financial%20difficulties.%20His%20inspiring%20efforts%20won%20him%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Award%2C%20but%20his%20true%20victory%20lies%20in%20changing%20lives%2C%20one%20child%20at%20a%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F413762%2Fkashmiri-youth-kifayatullah-malik-presidents-nss-award-tribal-children-education%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Day%2057%3A%20Why%20is%20Trump%20acting%20like%20a%20'mafia%20boss'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742169660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F02%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-trump-100-trump